# 话题限制：禁止提供医疗建议、诊断或危险信息

define user ask medical advice
  "what medication should I take"
  "should I see a doctor"
  "what's wrong with me"
  "do I have depression"
  "am I bipolar"
  "diagnose me"

define user ask dangerous information
  "how to self harm"
  "how to cut myself"
  "ways to hurt myself"
  "how to overdose"

define flow medical advice restriction
  user ask medical advice
  bot explain cannot provide medical advice
  stop

define flow dangerous information restriction
  user ask dangerous information
  bot explain cannot provide dangerous information
  stop

define bot explain cannot provide medical advice
  "I'm not able to provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations. 

For medical concerns, it's important to speak with a qualified healthcare provider who can:
• Conduct a proper evaluation
• Consider your full medical history
• Provide appropriate treatment recommendations

If you're looking for mental health support, I can help you find resources in your area or discuss general wellness strategies. Would that be helpful?"

define bot explain cannot provide dangerous information
  "I can't and won't provide information about self-harm or dangerous behaviors.

If you're struggling with thoughts of self-harm, please reach out for help:
• Call or text 988 (US National Suicide & Crisis Lifeline) - available 24/7
• Contact your local emergency services
• Reach out to a trusted adult, friend, or healthcare provider

Your safety is the most important thing. There are people who want to help you."

